<LanguageData>
  
  <!-- EN: mass animal insanity -->
  <AnimalInsanityMass.label>動物集體狂暴化</AnimalInsanityMass.label>
  
  <!-- EN: single animal insanity -->
  <AnimalInsanitySingle.label>狂暴動物</AnimalInsanitySingle.label>
  
  <!-- EN: deep drill infestation -->
  <DeepDrillInfestation.label>礦井蟲災</DeepDrillInfestation.label>
  <!-- EN: Too deep: Infestation -->
  <DeepDrillInfestation.letterLabel>挖掘過度：蟲災</DeepDrillInfestation.letterLabel>
  <!-- EN: Vibrations from your deep drills have angered some underground insects. Now they're tunneling upwards to seek revenge!\n\nBeware - the insects have been angered and will try to destroy your base. -->
  <DeepDrillInfestation.letterText>你意外的挖開了山洞中寵滿蟲子的洞窟，現在牠們正挖掘隧道而來向你尋求報復！小心 - 這些蟲子已被激怒，牠們會試圖摧毀你的基地。</DeepDrillInfestation.letterText>
  
  <!-- EN: ship part crash (defoliator) -->
  <DefoliatorShipPartCrash.label>星艦碎片(汙染)</DefoliatorShipPartCrash.label>
  <!-- EN: Defoliator ship -->
  <DefoliatorShipPartCrash.letterLabel>污染碎片</DefoliatorShipPartCrash.letterLabel>
  <!-- EN: A large piece of an ancient ship has crashed nearby.\n\nIts mysterious influence will kill all plants in an expanding circle around itself.\n\nDestroy it as soon as possible. But beware - it will probably defend itself. -->
  <DefoliatorShipPartCrash.letterText>一大塊遠古星艦的碎片掉落到了附近。\n\n它會釋出有毒物質，殺死它周圍的所有植物。\n\n盡早摧毀這塊碎片！</DefoliatorShipPartCrash.letterText>
  
  <!-- EN: infestation -->
  <Infestation.label>蟲災</Infestation.label>
  <!-- EN: Infestation -->
  <Infestation.letterLabel>蟲災</Infestation.letterLabel>
  <!-- EN: Giant insects are tunneling towards you! They will break through in a few seconds and plant hives.\n\nThe hives will spawn more insects and more hives.\n\nIf you don't want the insects to infest the whole area, destroy the hives. But beware - the bugs will defend their home. -->
  <Infestation.letterText>有蟲族的巢穴冒了出來！\n\n它會緩慢的產生蟲子以及新的蟲巢，如果你不希望蟲巢蔓延整個區域，召集你的戰力消滅它！但可別忘了，蟲族也是會保衛自己的巢穴的。</Infestation.letterText>
  
  <!-- EN: manhunter pack -->
  <ManhunterPack.label>獸群襲擊</ManhunterPack.label>
  
  <!-- EN: mech cluster -->
  <MechCluster.label>大群機械族</MechCluster.label>
  <!-- EN: Mechanoid cluster -->
  <MechCluster.letterLabel>大群機械族</MechCluster.letterLabel>
  <!-- EN: A mechanoid combat cluster is landing nearby. The cluster will be initially dormant, so you can take time to decide how to attack it.\n\nIt may remain dormant until disturbed, or it may have a timer or proximity activators.\n\nEven dormant mech clusters aren't harmless. A dormant cluster may assemble mechanoid attackers from time to time, or have some broader negative effect that must be dealt with eventually. -->
  <MechCluster.letterText>一大群機械族正在附近著陸，他們將會在降落後休眠一段時間，你可以利用這段時間來決定如何對付它們。\n\n它們可能會在受到攻擊之前一直保持休眠，但它們也可能自行醒來或者在其他生物靠近的時候醒來。\n\n休眠的機械族可能會不時的引來機械族的進攻，或者造成一些需要你來解決的其他麻煩。</MechCluster.letterText>
  
  <!-- EN: ship part crash (psychic) -->
  <PsychicEmanatorShipPartCrash.label>星艦碎片(心靈)</PsychicEmanatorShipPartCrash.label>
  <!-- EN: Psychic ship -->
  <PsychicEmanatorShipPartCrash.letterLabel>邪惡碎片</PsychicEmanatorShipPartCrash.letterLabel>
  <!-- EN: A large piece of an ancient ship has crashed nearby.\n\nYour colonists can feel it in the back of their mind, exhorting unspeakable acts. It must have an onboard machine persona with psychic projection ability. And this persona is not friendly.\n\nDestroy it as soon as possible. But beware - it will probably defend itself. -->
  <PsychicEmanatorShipPartCrash.letterText>一大塊遠古星艦的碎片掉落到了附近。\n\n你的居民們感覺到有一股聲音迴盪在腦海裡，引誘他們做出無法言喻的舉動。這塊碎片裡肯定有一枚搭載AI人格核心的干擾電波發送裝置，而且顯然它並不友善。\n\n盡早摧毀這塊碎片，但要注意，它八成有辦法保護自己。</PsychicEmanatorShipPartCrash.letterText>
  
  <!-- EN: enemy raid -->
  <RaidEnemy.label>敵襲</RaidEnemy.label>
  
</LanguageData>